oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Mavericks at the Ryman Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Ryman Auditorium (Nashville, Tenn.); Woodcuts (prints); Split Fountain Printing; Mavericks (Musical group);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (gray, split fountain, pink to yellow, and split fountain, green to yellow, on white) announcing the Mavericks with JD McPherson at the Ryman Auditorium on April 7. Poster features woodcuts. Poster background follows the process of reusing test sheets to produce a colorful college of imagery using historic woodblocks.
